*Theming*

With Talon's theme engine, pretty much anything is possible.

Create your own layouts, backgrounds, colors and more. If you are tired of the way the app looks, change it up at will!


Here is a section you can view other people's themes and post your own:

https://plus.google.com/u/0/communities/112468199526946242218/stream/c2f77fd2-23f2-4cb5-923e-6bb748fbcb69


Here it explains a little more about making your own, how it is done, and gives you some helpful links to do it:

https://plus.google.com/117432358268488452276/posts/eLwUTfWXYWX
